1954;;The Rocket Man;;American;;Oscar Rudolph;;Charles Coburn, Anne Francis;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Rocket_Man_(1954_film);;As a result of the sudden and unexplained appearance of a mysterious rocket man, a little boy comes into possession of a mysterious ray gun. But its not any ordinary ray gun but one that once its aimed and activated compels anyone caught in its beam to tell the truth. He uses it to prevent his orphanage from being foreclosed upon by creditors and to help a young couple fall in love.[4]